      <div class="cardWrap">
        <div class="resTitle">
          <p>GeorgiaGrown Pecan Shortbread Cookies</p>
        </div>
        <div class="shadowWrap">
        <div class="ingred">
          <img src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0816/7306/0668/files/AdobeStock_756492245.jpg?v=1730302603" />
          <div class="ingredBox">
            <div class="instructHead">
              <h6>Ingredients</h6>
            </div>
            
            <ul>
              <li>1 Cup salted butter</li>
              <li>1 Cup confectioner's sugar</li>
              <li>1 Teaspoon vanilla extract</li>
              <li>2 Cups all-purpose flour</li>
              <li>1 Tablespoon milk</li>
              <li>½ Cup toasted and finely chopped Georgia pecans</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="instruct">
          <div class="instructHead">
            <h6>Directions:</h6>
          </div>
          <div class="lineWrap">
            <div class="numb">
              <p>1</p>
            </div>
            <div class="line">
              <p>Heat oven to 350 degrees.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lineWrap">
            <div class="numb">
              <p>2</p>
            </div>
            <div class="line">
              <p>With a handheld or stand mixer, beat butter, sugar and vanilla until light and fluffy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lineWrap">
            <div class="numb">
              <p>3</p>
            </div>
            <div class="line">
              <p>Add flour and mix until crumbly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lineWrap">
            <div class="numb">
              <p>4</p>
            </div>
            <div class="line">
              <p>Add pecans and milk, mixing just until mixture comes together.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lineWrap">
            <div class="numb">
              <p>5</p>
            </div>
            <div class="line">
              <p>Tum out onto floured surface, and roll into a log. Slice into ¼ inch slices.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lineWrap">
            <div class="numb">
              <p>6</p>
            </div>
            <div class="line">
              <p>Bake about 15 minutes or until golden.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lineWrap">
            <div class="numb">
              <p>7</p>
            </div>
            <div class="line">
              <p>Let cool completely.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="lineWrap">
            <div class="numb">
              <p>8</p>
            </div>
            <div class="line">
              <p>Serve as is or create sandwich cookies with pecan butter and your favorite jelly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
        </div>
